Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.18,0:00:03.10,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's really warm!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.54,0:00:05.98,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Really feels like summer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.43,0:00:08.42,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you get your fill of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.42,0:00:10.99,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You won't be touching any warm \Nsurfaces for a while, after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:14.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:15.74,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.57,0:00:19.33,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this in Antarctica, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.26,0:00:26.75,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,Well, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.53,0:00:29.45,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to sail!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.10,0:00:31.35,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's done, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.35,0:00:32.26,Main,todo,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.55,0:00:34.76,Main,todo,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:37.76,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The boat left the land.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.98,0:00:44.77,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what this \Ntrip will mean in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:48.66,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be taking time off from \Nschool, missing tests...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:50.27,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It might even affect our entrance exams.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.69,0:00:57.78,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But as of now,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.07,0:01:01.28,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,we are no longer high school students \Nwho can never take a step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.77,0:01:08.99,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We are not 17-year-olds and 16-year-olds \Nwho try but accomplish nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.14,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's all ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.50,0:01:14.33,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.33,0:01:17.00,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The world really is big, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.18,0:01:21.04,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:23.97,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, guys, I'm taking a picture!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.51,0:01:25.90,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Look up here!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.29,0:01:28.98,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, say cheese!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.61,0:01:45.16,Show_Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2280,1225)}A Place Further Than the Universe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:07.45,Ep_Title,title,0000,0000,0000,,Howling,\NMaddening,\NScreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:07.45,Likes/Comments,title,0000,0000,0000,,20 Likes\N12 Comments
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.95,0:03:07.45,Hashtags,title,0000,0000,0000,,#LaundryDuty #MysterySolved #ArmyNice
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:10.21,sign_4495_32_High_school_girl,sign,0000,0000,0000,,High school girls are conducting\Nintervews!!\N^i     {\c&HE7EEEF&}.\N{\c&H374140&}*Please explain what your job is.\NOne person is enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.21,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:13.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I see! Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:16.35,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Very cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.35,0:03:19.17,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We're not live, so you can do it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.98,0:03:23.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We rocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:25.80,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They said the waves were \Ngonna get pretty rough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.25,0:03:28.54,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We really need to be efficient with our time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:31.45,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,They wanted us to help out later, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.45,0:03:33.56,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.03,0:03:36.44,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you wake me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.65,0:03:37.74,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.74,0:03:40.38,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Then you need to wake me harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:43.58,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:45.82,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Thirty minutes more!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.12,0:03:47.92,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen, at least!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.92,0:03:50.33,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. We'll wait outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.32,0:03:55.44,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Did she not have eyebrows?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.44,0:03:57.73,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,It's not uncommon among women.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:59.49,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd actually say it's typical.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.49,0:04:00.87,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.59,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.05,0:04:03.83,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,As we go further south,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.83,0:04:06.85,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be stopping at places in \Nthe ocean known as "stations"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.20,0:04:10.10,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,to gather bacteria and seawater.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.10,0:04:14.10,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,We have tons of equipment on \Nboard to help us with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.41,0:04:18.65,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,This is a water sampler and a CTD monitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:23.11,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! This is a water sampler \Nand a CTD monitor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.49,0:04:28.16,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be gathering rocks like these
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.16,0:04:30.62,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,and performing geological \Nsurveys in Antarctica.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.02,0:04:33.75,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,We'll investigate the stratum \Nseveral thousand meters down
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.42,0:04:33.75,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}The mic is too close!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.75,0:04:36.07,Main,yume,0000,0000,0000,,to learn more about the \Nconditions on primordial Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.07,0:04:37.88,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She has normal eyebrows, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.26,0:04:40.00,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Would you just listen to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:42.78,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no! Oh, no! Oh, no! \NWe're late! We're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.78,0:04:43.75,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Which way was it, again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:44.95,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.80,0:04:53.18,sign_6829_70_High_School_Girl,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(275,1)}High School Girls' room!!\NYou gotta {\c&H4EE8E2&}KNOCK
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.62,0:04:49.58,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.44,0:04:54.69,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.28,0:04:57.31,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah, we've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:04:59.12,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, dessert!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:00.69,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,You make that here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.00,0:05:04.04,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, with whatever we have, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:06.45,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you don't mind, start up on those.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.94,0:05:07.45,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Those?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:14.22,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This is why I wanted to bring a peeler!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.22,0:05:14.91,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Rin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:20.67,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,There are still so many more to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.10,0:05:22.92,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But this kind of thing is fun, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.22,0:05:25.67,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You like grunt work, huh, Kimari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.91,0:05:42.30,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like it takes the four of \Nyou just to reach one horsepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.30,0:05:43.32,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Are we that slow?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.90,0:05:47.07,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's clear you don't help \Nout at home very often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.07,0:05:49.65,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Still, don't rush yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.65,0:05:51.20,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,We don't want you getting hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.68,0:05:52.20,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.58,0:05:54.37,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I am a pro, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:56.41,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you a cook somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.41,0:05:58.29,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm usually a lunch lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.29,0:06:01.17,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm constantly thinking \Nup and preparing dishes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.50,0:06:03.55,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,for picky eaters like you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.88,0:06:06.80,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, work hard, \Nso you can get up on deck soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:08.30,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Get up on deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.55,0:06:18.24,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}From 1100 hours to 1700 hours, training is \Npermitted on-deck. Counterclockwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.24,0:06:18.81,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.61,0:06:21.61,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,It means we're allowed to train topside.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.61,0:06:24.29,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, we can go \Noutside and get some exercise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:25.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Exercise?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:27.49,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take you up when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.41,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,It's sort of a duty for expedition members.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:34.93,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.68,0:06:37.82,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,W-We're going to run here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.82,0:06:38.51,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.20,0:06:39.37,Main,toshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:50.24,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,If they announce clockwise, \Nyou'd go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.24,0:06:53.45,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,If they announce counterclockwise, \Nyou go that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:55.89,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,The direction changes by day, so be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.89,0:06:56.43,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.45,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,About how long do we have to run?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.45,0:07:01.28,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,There's no particular rule.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.28,0:07:05.28,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,But as we've told you over and over, \Nstamina is crucial on an expedition.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.59,0:07:09.51,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,You might be working all day \Nin sub-zero conditions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.86,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,so you need strong bodies \Nto meet the challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.08,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Mom was always exercising, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.53,0:07:17.48,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,If you run out of stamina and pass out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.48,0:07:19.18,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,not only will you not contribute anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.18,0:07:22.15,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,you'll be an active drag \Non the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.15,0:07:24.94,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to get to \NAntarctica to be a drag, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.94,0:07:25.56,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.00,0:07:26.80,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,She's fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.30,0:07:31.52,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! We'll do our best, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.59,0:07:33.30,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:36.41,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san doesn't realize, does she?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.41,0:07:38.31,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,She'll catch on soon enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.08,0:07:53.10,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.10,0:07:55.24,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.24,0:07:58.84,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Why... is it... so big?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.84,0:08:02.06,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You've walked around here \Ncountless times, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:05.49,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But... everyone else... goes so fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:12.49,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Even she can run that fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.49,0:08:15.03,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like a scientist,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.03,0:08:17.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,but I guess she still has tons of stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.71,0:08:20.57,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We're going.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.17,0:08:24.11,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:28.05,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.87,0:08:32.99,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,By the time we get to Antarctica, \Nwe'll be Amazons!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.24,0:08:34.82,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be that easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.82,0:08:36.62,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, last one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.65,0:08:42.95,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It itches!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:44.62,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,My nose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.38,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzu, can you not lift your arms?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:53.01,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,If you do anything, I will just kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.01,0:08:55.51,sign_12780_146_I_will_kill_you_,sign,0000,0000,0000,,I will kill you ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:58.01,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You idiots! You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:08:59.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a seawater bath...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.32,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It's pretty big, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.32,0:09:03.02,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely worth experiencing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.58,0:09:05.62,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Would you get out already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.74,0:09:10.27,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Seawater is more permeating than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.51,0:09:12.37,Main,shiri,0000,0000,0000,,My hair is so crusty...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.45,Main,shiri,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's why everyone cuts their hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.45,0:09:16.52,Main,shiri,0000,0000,0000,,And the men shave their heads...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, maybe we should cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:19.53,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'll cut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.23,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The boat has barber facilities, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.23,0:09:24.00,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Not even if the fate of \Nthe world depended on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.00,0:09:24.96,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Ditto.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.48,0:09:29.00,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,How come? I'm good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:31.30,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I cut my own bangs all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.98,0:09:35.47,Italics,hina,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the mystery...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.47,0:09:36.62,Italics,shira,0000,0000,0000,,...is solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.62,0:09:37.22,Italics,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.22,Italics,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,...her hair looks like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.82,0:09:41.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.00,0:09:44.01,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Provisions ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.45,0:09:45.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.25,0:09:46.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No way! Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.23,Main,sign,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.23,sign_14068_172_Missed_meal_card,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Missed meal cards go here | Already eaten: Black
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.23,sign_14068_173_Samejima_Yasumot,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Samejima Yasumoto\NYumiko    Honami
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.02,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm all sticky!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.02,0:09:53.44,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Because you didn't wash off \Nproperly in the shower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.98,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't have time!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.98,0:09:57.62,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, meat and potatoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.99,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Are these the ones we peeled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.43,0:10:03.04,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Have we forgotten to do anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:05.95,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Dinner, bath... laundry?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.63,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we have to do that \Nat a certain time, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:11.37,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's because you two were \Nplaying around in the bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:12.75,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Take responsibility and go do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.75,0:10:14.96,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, but what about our dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:18.72,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But didn't we pick someone to do it \Nbecause it seemed easy to forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.88,0:10:20.44,Main,hian,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:21.43,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.67,0:10:24.19,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall, we did rock-paper-scissors...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.15,0:10:26.73,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,sign_15027_190_Laundry_Room__Ba,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Laundry Room  Bath
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:29.73,sign_15027_191_Regarding_use_of,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Regarding use of fresh water\N{\fs12}Fresh water baths permitted during ship-wide training\N(Salt water baths are allowed, too!)\N{\fs16\c&H2F3E75&}Please try to conserve water ♥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.73,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.00,0:10:31.80,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "that'll do it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.80,0:10:34.10,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You actually sat there \Nand ate your whole meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:36.15,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I still made it in time, \Nso what's the problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.48,0:10:43.24,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.83,0:10:45.42,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,She must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.42,0:10:48.10,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,They kept us busy a lot \Nlonger than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.10,0:10:49.55,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, true...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.55,0:10:51.15,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,And it all starts again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.61,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You think we'll hold out?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:55.24,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to do our best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.24,0:10:57.17,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.26,0:11:01.49,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Feel sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.14,0:11:08.25,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I feel... sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:15.44,sign_16063_206_When_using_the_t,sign,0000,0000,0000,,When using the toilet,\Nturn this valve\Ncounterclockwise\Nto flush.\NAfter flushing,\Nplease close\Nthe valve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.94,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Going to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.94,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The world is spinning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.32,0:11:21.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Don't talk. If you talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.61,0:11:26.22,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.65,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.03,0:11:31.58,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You're really seasick, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.34,0:11:35.41,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But we were totally fine before.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.85,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,We took medicine for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.85,0:11:39.53,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't that wear off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.73,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It can wear off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.72,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,It's medicine. Of course \Nit'll wear off eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.99,0:11:45.25,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.71,0:11:50.31,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been on a boat this long. \NI didn't even think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.60,0:11:51.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Hinata, you idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.29,0:11:53.81,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I the idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.35,0:11:56.19,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,You need to take medicine \Nand get a good night's rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.67,0:11:58.70,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,Then have a proper meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.41,0:12:01.09,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,I know you probably don't have an appetite,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.09,0:12:04.31,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,and you're afraid that if you \Neat it'll just come back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:06.83,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,But if you don't eat, \Nyou'll just keep losing stamina.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:11.30,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,If it gets bad enough, we might \Nhave to give you an IV supplement.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:12.82,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:15.68,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, none of your \Ntraining will mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:17.21,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.13,0:12:19.89,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Provisions ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.87,0:12:28.70,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Remember what Kanae-san said?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:31.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't want to be a drag in Antarctica,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.81,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,we have to eat, whether we like it or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:47.28,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It all came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.76,0:12:50.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yuzuki-chan, did it all come up for you, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.65,0:12:52.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.60,0:12:54.93,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Stop rocking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.31,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Just stop for a little bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.31,0:12:59.52,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I think it is stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:00.30,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.50,0:13:02.91,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,They said they're collecting seawater.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.91,0:13:04.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,And still...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.16,0:13:07.80,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yumiko-san said we'd get \Nused to it eventually.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.80,0:13:09.30,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But it's not happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:15.81,sign_18925_246_Great_Knot_Tying,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Great Knot-Tying Competition{check}\N{\c&H343843&}Winning team gets a steak dinner!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:15.81,sign_18925_247_Sizzle_sizzle_si,sign,0000,0000,0000,,Sizzle sizzle sizzle! Pictured: the steaks from three years ago\NThis time, it's {\c&H513BA7&}meat{\c&H474A47&}! {\c&H513BA7&}Meat{\c&H474A47&}!! {\c&H513BA7&}Meat{\c&H474A47&}!!!\NMeat is the great motivator!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:15.81,sign_18925_248_If_you_re_planni,sign,0000,0000,0000,,If you're planning on winning, please bring your \Nprovided army -n-i-c-e- knife, please.\N The steaks are not pre-cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.30,0:13:15.81,sign_18925_249_You_were_given_a,sign,0000,0000,0000,,You were given an army \Nknife for cutting steak
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.94,0:13:13.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}They've probably been on boats so often
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:15.14,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}their semicircular canals are busted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:19.10,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}From 0800 hours to 1400 hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.10,0:13:22.98,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}training is permitted on-deck. Clockwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.42,0:13:24.50,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,What'll we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.18,0:13:34.08,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's no way I can run...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.52,0:13:38.04,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a little better outside, \Nwith the wind, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.70,0:13:42.55,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I could probably manage it \Nif not for the rocking...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.82,0:13:51.94,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see the whales...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:53.56,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Whales? Can you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.47,0:13:56.94,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,They said earlier that they were in sight.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.18,0:14:01.65,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Can you see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.37,0:14:05.38,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Tamaki-san, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.38,0:14:06.59,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.59,0:14:07.57,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,There's one right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:16.84,Main,nobu,0000,0000,0000,,You see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.02,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,She self-destructed just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.02,0:14:23.34,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Because she was focusing \Non a single point, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.34,0:14:26.33,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Lay off. Just thinking about \Nit makes me want to puke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.33,0:14:29.89,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,There they are. Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.89,0:14:32.15,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,I looked in your room earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.15,0:14:37.10,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,and it looked like you weren't \Nready at all. Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.10,0:14:38.23,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.02,0:14:40.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,53 degrees?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.98,0:14:44.73,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Though we set that record a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.17,0:14:49.42,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,The last time I came here, \Nit felt to me like we rocked so far,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.42,0:14:52.70,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,this desk was up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.70,0:14:53.49,Main,both,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.15,0:14:58.50,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to Antarctica, \Nyou must surpass these things...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.27,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,The howling 40 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.27,0:15:03.50,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,The maddening 50 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:06.63,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,The screaming 60 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:10.26,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.78,0:15:12.23,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's about latitudes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.71,0:15:14.76,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Earth is a water planet, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.24,0:15:19.45,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It spins on its axis, and that \Ncreates wind and water currents.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:22.50,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But Earth has continents,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:26.12,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,so those block the currents and weaken them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:29.20,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,But around this area of \Nthe southern hemisphere,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:31.98,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,there's no land in the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.98,0:15:34.55,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,so there's nothing to interrupt the current.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.55,0:15:39.40,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Mom said they were going to plow \Ntheir way right through it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.40,0:15:41.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,How long will it take?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.36,0:15:45.13,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know all the \Ndetails, but pretty long.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.70,0:15:51.01,Main,hona,0000,0000,0000,,Your insides will go woo, \Nlike on a roller coaster!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:56.10,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,A roller coaster? I like those, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.66,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,But do you want to go on one now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.33,0:16:06.44,Main,muka,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:11.95,Main,todo,0000,0000,0000,,Though I like this kind of thing... \Nthe feeling, like I'm fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.45,0:16:16.45,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,I'm falling!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.13,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That was the biggest one yet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.13,0:16:29.99,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I think that was about 15 degrees.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.99,0:16:31.08,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.05,0:16:34.72,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Here it comes, here it comes, \Nhere it comes, here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:43.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I floated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.81,0:16:45.06,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,My body floated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.06,0:16:49.46,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better stay in bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.46,0:16:52.82,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But the blood is rushing to my head...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.93,0:16:55.97,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.97,0:16:57.71,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.71,0:16:59.16,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm dizzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:02.29,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,No getting to sleep tonight, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:04.29,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.24,0:17:16.05,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You think we'll really make it to Antarctica?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.56,0:17:19.56,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Of course we will. \NWe're on a boat going there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.13,0:17:22.42,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.42,0:17:25.56,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,but we might not be able to \Ndo anything once we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.93,0:17:36.07,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone has so much stamina, \Nand they can handle the boat...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.95,0:17:42.20,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like we're completely \Ndifferent organisms.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:45.33,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Then we have to become stronger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.98,0:17:48.75,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You really think we can be like them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.30,0:17:51.17,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to do our best, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:53.26,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have any other choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.89,0:17:55.47,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.84,0:17:59.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We always had a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.58,0:18:02.60,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,But we chose to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.60,0:18:03.86,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Kimari-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.44,0:18:06.98,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,We chose this ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.06,0:18:15.11,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Well said!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:17.61,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.32,0:18:21.12,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,The toilet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.62,0:18:28.07,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'm getting used to throwing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.07,0:18:29.11,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.11,0:18:32.38,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,I'll eat anything! I'll puke anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.81,0:18:39.34,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,That was an actual hill.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.56,0:18:42.14,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, when I get home I can tell them...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.54,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,expedition ships are amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.54,0:18:47.35,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll tell them it was really fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.40,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,You must be joking!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.40,0:18:50.73,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.01,0:18:54.74,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that when this trip \Nis over, that's how we'll feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.16,0:19:12.96,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to go outside for a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:14.71,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds good!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.05,0:19:16.71,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:18.81,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:35.32,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's pitch black!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.55,0:19:38.07,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,This is the ocean we're crossing, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.47,0:19:41.82,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,To a continent of ice protected \Nby storms and raging waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:45.08,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,We really did choose to go there, didn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.28,0:19:51.96,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? Rain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.46,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,It's salty! It's the waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.59,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,You're right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.55,0:19:59.59,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It's salty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.17,0:20:14.15,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling better?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.40,0:20:16.35,Main,kima,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're totally fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.35,0:20:18.15,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Because we saw the whales yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:21.40,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like you've gotten used to the boat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.86,0:20:22.53,Main,all,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.91,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:27.79,Main,yumi,0000,0000,0000,,Once we make landfall, \Nyou're gonna get landsick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.68,0:20:29.44,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:31.04,Italics,vo,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Left ten degrees, five miles!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.63,0:20:36.96,Main,mari,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:41.11,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.11,0:20:42.90,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,No birds.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.53,0:20:46.76,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,The view is a single sheet of blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.72,0:20:52.52,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I strain my eyes, \Nbut the horizon is all I can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.70,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was probably hearing \Nthe sounds of the boat,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.47,0:21:02.54,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,but that overwhelming scenery seemed \Nto render everything silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.91,0:21:09.19,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,I was looking out on an infinite \Nworld reminiscent of outer space.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:12.64,Main,yuzu,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:14.34,Main,hina,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.00,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.03,0:21:19.25,Main,shira,0000,0000,0000,,Those are...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.11,0:21:35.14,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,In that moment, we knew for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.90,0:21:40.30,Italics,kima,0000,0000,0000,,It really lay ahead... Antarctica!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.42,0:21:45.84,Main,kana,0000,0000,0000,,We're back, aren't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.16,0:21:51.01,Main,todo,0000,0000,0000,,Though it'll be a long time before \Nwe're even opening the front door.
